# Terminal and general commands
- the token "&&" is not a valid seperator in my terminal version
- to run my backend: `poetry run uvicorn backend.main:app --reload`
- to run frontend (must be in /frontend dir): `npm run dev`


# Testing
## Backend
- run all tests: `poetry run pytest backend/tests`
- Run specific test file: `poetry run pytest backend/tests/<specific_test_file>.py -v`

## Frontend  
- run all tests once: `npm run test:run`
- run tests in watch mode: `npm run test`
- run with UI interface: `npm run test:ui`
- run with coverage report: `npm run test:coverage`


